item.title: Free Stock Footage Fire Torch
item.description: This is a free looping stock video asset of fire burning. You can use it in your video projects. Just import it into your video project and set the blend mode to screen. It will cut out the black background. This is a royalty free, license free fire stock video footage asset for use in all your projects.
